Published Friday, 2026-01-02, including PRs merged Friday, 2025-12-26 through Thursday, 2026-01-01.
’Щ@d749d9f568f995fbbadd791c1ab0b25f7a5990d79e9cbd5ac7488a4eb1d7db4dЩТTitle: title: 'This week in Nushell #332'
Path: Highlights
Content:
A long awaited feature has landed - You can now pipe a value into the 
``let``
 command to set a variable within a pipeline! Thanks @fdncred!
